{
  "stem": "8786.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, the filling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My own father's and somebody else's filling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was crying, because in the Psalms, King David has a passage in the Psalms and they raffle out my clothing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in such terrible condition that they gave up on him and they were raffling, selling out his clothing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is what happened to me because in Hebrew it says, [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were raffling out my clothing and they were dividing my-- let's call it [YIDDISH] because I was full of lice and there's nothing there valuable, but people were just plain subhuman.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- the thinking was not normal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So if somebody was taken away for no reason.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on, I've seen worse things, because in Gunskirchen you could see human flesh being sold.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Sold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just given away for something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I've seen those cutoff bodies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could see that people were not-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, we arrived to-- and it was a horrible feeling to try to get better my junks.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I got back my things and we are back in the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a day later then we started to go to Malthausen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Malthausen was a-- what shall I tell you about Malthausen?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Malthausen was one of the most famous horrible places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We found over there a huge mountain like.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was no trees, just plain people and a tent, because all the regular barracks was already full.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Full.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was already a get together from those places, from the smaller camps which couldn't be continued because they were all gathering together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is like a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], which means--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gathering point.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From all the smaller camps in the around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was Ebensee was also a big one.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
